{"tid":1946073,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際戰線】英國下議院動議收集濫暴黑隊高官名單！4月7日截止","createTime":"2020-03-27T11:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T20:31:32.000Z","uid":138409,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"6a437a513893e093597f9e4c84177ecfa4a7c668","tid":1946073,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/photos/a.497270963815064/1383819251826893/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fphotos%2Fa.497270963815064%2F1383819251826893%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=1851b5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/photos/a.497270963815064/1383819251826893/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n 【🇬🇧英國下議院動議收集濫暴黑隊高官名單｜黃之鋒：香港小組收集緊資料 4月7日截止啦📣】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2SL7ur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2SL7ur.png&h=ecb0dd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共連番破壞「一國兩制」，動用黑警血腥壓鎮抗爭者，英國下議院岩岩上咗份「早期動議（Early Day Motions）」，話極度擔心中共破壞《聯合聲明》，要求英國當局盡早制訂《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁踐踏人權人士，仲要求 #外交部著手鎖定有份鎮壓抗爭的香港警隊及政府高層，即便一有制裁法案，立即採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 Joshua Wong 話，全賴英國戰線手足一直以來嘅努力，今次下議院罕有地有條早期動議，促請外交部就《人權問責法》和制裁黑警及高官表態，可見國際戰線深耕細作，一定會換嚟成果。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">他又話，以此同時，英國國會跨黨派香港小組早於一月起，已經收集緊黑警點樣打壓人道支援人員，#四月七日就截止啦，大家快啲幫手畀料啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n報料連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkinquiry.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkinquiry.org%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=eec37f12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkinquiry.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n早期動議<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UpYDhH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UpYDhH&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=a745e41e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UpYDhH</a><br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n💰支持眾志 <a href=\"http://www.demosisto.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.demosisto.hk%2Fdonation&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=dc26ccf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.demosisto.hk/donation</a>"},{"pid":"e758eb6143406f46ba64451e96cd982ad06b3015","tid":1946073,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:41:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"734b671d499ebc0265a4996d15c6710cac1eec74","tid":1946073,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac98ea957cc02bee64678578e10f546d8b10de04","tid":1946073,"uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=7d0247d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a><br />\n<br />\n齊曬 定要當事人"},{"pid":"c3ff8e0db67c9da7dab56c4fa95737e0dc777cda","tid":1946073,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b430f0e32ffdc77596f52c3e1aa984006ef59fad","tid":1946073,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:43:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc3bf8d5dba655d5646d1f1f9c3c661499f8436f","tid":1946073,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac98ea957cc02bee64678578e10f546d8b10de04","tid":1946073,"uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=7d0247d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a><br />\n<br />