a.cx%2Fi%2Fp2SL7ur.png&h=ecb0dd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共連番破壞「一國兩制」，動用黑警血腥壓鎮抗爭者，英國下議院岩岩上咗份「早期動議（Early Day Motions）」，話極度擔心中共破壞《聯合聲明》，要求英國當局盡早制訂《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁踐踏人權人士，仲要求 #外交部著手鎖定有份鎮壓抗爭的香港警隊及政府高層，即便一有制裁法案，立即採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 Joshua Wong 話，全賴英國戰線手足一直以來嘅努力，今次下議院罕有地有條早期動議，促請外交部就《人權問責法》和制裁黑警及高官表態，可見國際戰線深耕細作，一定會換嚟成果。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">他又話，以此同時，英國國會跨黨派香港小組早於一月起，已經收集緊黑警點樣打壓人道支援人員，#四月七日就截止啦，大家快啲幫手畀料啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n報料連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkinquiry.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkinquiry.org%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=eec37f12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkinquiry.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n早期動議<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UpYDhH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UpYDhH&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=a745e41e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UpYDhH</a><br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n💰支持眾志 <a href=\"http://www.demosisto.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.demosisto.hk%2Fdonation&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=dc26ccf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.demosisto.hk/donation</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"美國人權基金會正發起眾籌，希望成立「香港專案小組」，全力打聯合國戰線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1907404/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1907404/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2795b599fa4d1815e6462bee3549f4d5275b8cae","tid":1946073,"uid":51938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"哇 好重要!!! 推!!!"},{"pid":"a77cabb09fb0c8d656bdbf999bc56ac19f9e4ce0","tid":1946073,"uid":172227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}